00:06:12.300 --> 00:06:17.180
So in our closing words
really, a few impressions.

00:06:17.180 --> 00:06:20.895
I mean, listening
to Dan's talk, there

00:06:20.895 --> 00:06:22.380
was a lot to take
on board there.

00:06:22.380 --> 00:06:25.210
